platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Pok Pok Playrooms married founders set out to create a kids app parents wouldnt have to mute in a restaurantand to the delight of grown-up diners everywhere, they did it. Pok Pok Playroom is a free-play feast for little senses: There are switches to flip, gears to grind, and blobs to plop together, all drawn and designed by hand to make the app feel like a tactile, handcrafted toy. Endlessly inventive but never overwhelming, its a master class in how a simple app can sometimes feel the most advanced.
